## Quarterly review

::agent_task{id="quarterly-review-task"}
Every quarter, re-evaluate gross margin, order backlog, China exposure, and EUV demand. Update the `confidence` attribute on each claim if material changes are observed. Add a fresh `evidence` block citing the source document.
::

## Notes

> The thesis is intentionally short. The point of Noma is that the *structure* — not the prose volume — is what makes a thesis useful to revisit and to feed into an LLM at review time.
